Classic Game Room reviews CIRCUS ATARI for Atari 2600 from 1980 (text label, the picture one is actually 1978!), a paddle controller game where you bounce clowns off a teeter totter into colored balloons for points!

CGR Circus Atari YouTube review has Circus Atari gameplay recorded from Atari 2600 for this video review. Played with the paddle controllers. Available as a text label and picture label cartridge.
